[22.5941823,"o","\n============================================================\r\n                ===[RACES OF THE WORLD]===\r\n\n(1) Human: A versatile, diverse, and populous people. Found\r\n           nearly everywhere in the world of Kaelos.\r\n(2) Dwarf: Stocky and strong folk of the mountains, notable\r\n           for producing warriors, clerics and stonemasons.\r\n(3) Elf:   Mysterious and ancient race, known to many as the\r\n           Firstborn; they are graceful, yet often austere.\r\n(4) Gnome: Merry tinkerers of unusually small stature, known\r\n           for baking, poetry, and enjoying the good life.\r\n(5) Centaur: Wise and noble beings; half-horse and half-man,\r\n           they are often found in forests and in the wild.\r\n============================================================\r\n\nInput a number:"]
