[24.849116,"o","\n"]
[25.349116,"o","\nYou shall be a Gnome.\r"]
[25.3525057,"o","\n"]
[25.3530301,"o","\n============================================================\r\n                ===[GUILDS OF THE WORLD]===\r\n\n(1) Warrior: Champion of sword and shield, the warrior relies\u001b[1C\r\n             on physical prowess to withstand enemies and\u001b[1C\r\n             deliver crushing strikes, excelling in melee.\r\n(2) Cleric:  Gifted with powers by the gods, the cleric\u001b[1C\r\n             excels in channeling holy might to struggle\u001b[1C\r\n             against evil.\r\n(3) Rogue:   Masters of stealth, the rogue thrives in\u001b[1C\r\n             mystery, dancing through battle with deadly\r\n             precision.\r\n(4) Wizard:  Harnessing elemental power, the wizard uses\u001b[1C\r\n             magical arts to strike from a distance, though\r\n             they themselves are often weak in hand-to-hand.\r\n(5) Ranger:  Stalking the wilds on the edge of civilization,\r\n             rangers are the ultimate survivalists, often\u001b[1C\r\n             braving treacherous terrain and deadly beasts.\r\n============================================================\r\n\nInput a number:"]
