[26.3664801,"o","4"]
[27.1255576,"o","\r"]
[27.6255576,"o","\n"]
[28.1255576,"o","\nYou shall be a Wizard.\r"]
[28.1265754,"o","\n"]
[28.6265754,"o","\nYour six stats are STR, DEX, CON, INT, WIS, and CHA.\r"]
[29.1265754,"o","\nSTR: Your strength, which affects your carrying capacity and weapon attacks.\r"]
[29.6265754,"o","\nDEX: Your dexterity, which affects some weapon attacks and your defense.\r"]
[29.6271416,"o","\nCON: Your constitution, which affects your endurance and health.\r"]
[30.1271416,"o","\nINT: Your intelligence, which affects your ability for intellectual work.\r\nWIS: Your wisdom, which affects your perception, intuition, and insight.\r"]
[30.1276383,"o","\nCHA: Your charisma, which affects your ability to persuade or trick.\r\nEach is rolled with 3d6. You may reroll your results once.\r"]
[30.6276383,"o","\nAfterwards, you'll assign each value to a stat of your choice.\r"]
[31.1276383,"o","\n"]
[31.6276383,"o","\nYou rolled the following values (highest to lowest):\r"]
[32.1276383,"o","\n  1. 13\r"]
[32.6276383,"o","\n  2. 12\r"]
[33.1276383,"o","\n  3. 10\r"]
