[88.1093051,"o","\nUsage:\r\n   [command]\r\n\nCommand list:\u001b[1C\r\n  auth           Authrization to asciinema.org.\r\n  convert-to-gif Converts an asciinema cast to gif.\r\n  cut            Removes a certain range of time frames.\r\n  play           Plays a record.\r\n  quantize       Updates the cast delays following quantization ranges.\r\n  record         Creates a record.\r\n  speed          Updates the cast speed by a certain factor.\r\n  upload         Uploads a record file to asciinema.org.\r\n  version        Shows version info of acast.\r\n\nAdditional Commands:\r\n  completion     Generate the autocompletion script for the specified shell\r\n  help           Help about any command\r\n\nFlags:\r\n  -h, --help   help for this command\r\n\nUse \" [command] --help\" for more information about a command."]
